OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779210357
OL,3,CLorry driver on video call to his wife
OL,4,Cjailed for killing father in crash
OL,6,FA lorry driver who killed a father-of-
OL,7,Ftwo on the motorway when he crashed
OL,8,Finto his car while on a video call to
OL,9,Fhis wife has been jailed.
OL,11,FZvonko Tomisa was travelling at
OL,12,Fapproximately 55mph before he tried to
OL,13,Fbrake one second before he hit Arran
OL,14,FMcManus's car in standstill traffic on
OL,15,Fthe M20 in Kent on November 25 last
OL,16,Fyear.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
