PN,41802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779210357
OL,3,CLorry driver on video call to his wife
OL,4,Cjailed for killing father in crash
OL,6,FAt Maidstone Crown Court on Monday,
OL,7,Fthe court heard how there were
OL,8,Fmultiple incoming and outgoing calls,
OL,9,Fmessages and video calls from Tomisa's
OL,10,Fphone in the hour before the crash.
OL,12,FThe 58-year-old was on a video call
OL,13,Fwith his wife immediately before and
OL,14,Fat the time he crashed into the local
OL,15,Ffootball coach's Nissan Qashqai car at
OL,16,Faround 48mph.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779210357
OL,3,CLorry driver on video call to his wife
OL,4,Cjailed for killing father in crash
OL,6,FMr McManus, 36, who was on his way to
OL,7,Fwork, was crushed and sustained
OL,8,Finjuries that were "not survivable" as
OL,9,Fhe was forced into another lorry in
OL,10,Ffront of him, the court heard.
OL,12,FTomisa, of Videovec, in Croatia, was
OL,13,Faided by an interpreter as he was
OL,14,Fsentenced to 11 years in prison for
OL,15,Fdeath by dangerous driving and banned
OL,16,Ffrom driving for 14 years and four
OL,17,Fmonths.
OL,26,@pD@TOUpD@cO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779210357
OL,3,CLorry driver on video call to his wife
OL,4,Cjailed for killing father in crash
OL,6,FThere had been signs for drivers to
OL,7,Fslow down to 50mph more than 1.5 miles
OL,8,Fbefore Tomisa crashed into Mr McManus,
OL,9,Fbecause of a build-up of traffic that
OL,10,Fmay have been linked to an earlier
OL,11,Fincident that morning.
OL,13,FSentencing him, Judge Catherine Moore
OL,14,Fsaid: "It is abundantly clear your
OL,15,Fentirely senseless actions meant your
OL,16,Fattention was distracted.
OL,18,F"You plainly assumed your driving
OL,19,Fwould be unaffected by your mobile
OL,20,Ftelephone use and that somehow the
OL,21,Frules did not apply to you.
OL,26,@vD@GOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779210357
OL,3,CLorry driver on video call to his wife
OL,4,Cjailed for killing father in crash
OL,6,F"You were not concentrating on the
OL,7,Froad, your failure to do so had tragic
OL,8,Fand entirely avoidable consequences."
OL,10,FA statement from Mr McManus's partner,
OL,11,FAshleigh Devlin, paid tribute to him
OL,12,Fas clever, witty and "always making us
OL,13,Flaugh", adding: "Even mundane moments
OL,14,Flike shopping in Tesco or cleaning the
OL,15,Fhouse were fun with him.
OL,17,F"He was one of the good ones for sure."
OL,19,FShe added their family has lost a
OL,20,Fdevoted father, active mentor and
OL,21,F"central figure in our community".
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@eO]tD@VOUuD@FO]uD@QOUyD@AOUyD@
OL,26,AgO]}D@AOU}D@aO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
