FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779210357
OL,3,CLorry driver on video call to his wife
OL,4,Cjailed for killing father in crash
OL,6,FOn behalf of Tomisa, the court heard
OL,7,Fhe deeply regrets "all his decisions"
OL,8,Fon that date and is deeply remorseful
OL,9,Fand traumatised by the events.
OL,11,FHis defence barrister told the court
OL,12,FTomisa accepts he was "deeply
OL,13,Fdistracted" on that date, mainly
OL,14,Fbecause his wife was having an
OL,15,Foperation.
OL,17,FBut Judge Moore said: "It may well
OL,18,Fhave been you were discussing a
OL,19,Fmedical matter or a matter about which
OL,20,Fthere was some anxiety, but that is no
OL,21,Fexcuse."
OL,26,@oD@SOUoD@eO]tD@WOUuD@KO]yD@WOU}D@HO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
