OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779210357
OL,3,CLorry driver on video call to his wife
OL,4,Cjailed for killing father in crash
OL,6,FIn a letter from the defendant read
OL,7,Fout to court, he said he took
OL,8,Fresponsibility for everything that
OL,9,Fhappened.
OL,11,FHe said: "There is not a word that can
OL,12,Fdilute the pain and the loss that
OL,13,Ffamily went through after the person
OL,14,Flost their life.
OL,16,F"I am carrying the weight of this
OL,17,Ftragedy every day and I'm truly
OL,18,Fcompassionate and empathise with their
OL,19,Fsuffering.
OL,26,@sD@JOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
