OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779210357
OL,3,CLorry driver on video call to his wife
OL,4,Cjailed for killing father in crash
OL,6,F"It was never my intention to cause
OL,7,Fharm to anyone and especially with
OL,8,Fthese consequences."
OL,10,FTomisa had changed his plea to guilty
OL,11,Fto death by dangerous driving on April
OL,12,F9 this year.
OL,14,FThe court heard he had been a
OL,15,Fprofessional truck driver since the
OL,16,Fage of 20 and for most of his 38-year
OL,17,Fcareer he had driven on foreign roads.
OL,19,FHe had arrived in the UK via Dover
OL,20,Fabout an hour before the fatal
OL,21,Fcollision.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@TO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779210357
OL,3,CLorry driver on video call to his wife
OL,4,Cjailed for killing father in crash
OL,6,FKent Police chief inspector Craig West
OL,7,Fsaid Mr McManus's death was
OL,8,F"completely avoidable".
OL,10,FHe said: "Mr McManus was a huge part
OL,11,Fof the Ashford community and his death
OL,12,Fhas had a devastating impact.
OL,14,F"If anything good can come from this
OL,15,Ftragic incident, I hope it's that
OL,16,Fpeople look at Mr McManus's death and
OL,17,Frealise the detrimental impacts that
OL,18,Fcan be caused by using a phone while
OL,19,Fdriving.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@VO]rD@JOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
