OL,3,CLorry driver on video call to his wife
OL,4,Cjailed for killing father in crash
OL,6,F"We have a zero tolerance policy for
OL,7,Fthis at Kent Police, and will do
OL,8,Feverything we can to ensure no other
OL,9,Ffamily has to go through what Mr
OL,10,FMcManus's family is having to endure."
OL,12,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,13,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,14,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,15,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,16,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,17,Fbelow...
